    "notes": [
      "One platform group entry expands into antiship_systems container rows; platform_group, platform_group_index, container_capacity, and mainline_mobility are stored as DB columns (Option B-lite).",
      "group_sizes and to_assignments arrays are index-aligned and 1-based for platform_group_index in exports.",
      "type_id values map to existing antiship_system_types IDs; fresh defaults use IDs 3, 5, 6 and 16-24. 2026 OOB update: type 2 (Missile Patrol Boats) split into Kwang Hua VI (16), Tuo Chiang (17), Anping (18); type 1 (Destroyers and Frigates) split into Keelung (19), Cheng Kung (20), Kang Ding (21), Chi Yang (22); type 4 (Mobile Coastal AShM) split into HF launchers (23) and Harpoon launchers (24).",
      "mainline_mobility is metadata-only; IJFS runtime uses ijfs_profile.mobility."
    ]
  },
